title: Chicken and Corn Tortilla Soup
ingredients: ['6 tablespoons vegetable oil', '8 corn tortillas, coarsely chopped', '6 cloves garlic, finely chopped', '25g fresh coriander, chopped', '1 onion, chopped', '2 (400g) tins chopped tomatoes', '2 tablespoons ground cumin', '1 tablespoon chilli powder', '3 bay leaves', '1.5 litres chicken stock', '1 teaspoon salt', '1/2 teaspoon ground cayenne pepper', '5 boneless chicken breast fillets, cooked']
